            <h1>Metroplex's Office Refreshment Management System</h1>
            
            <div class="genline">
            	<p>Metroplex's Office Refreshment Management System is built around software modules that can 
run in any combination, to provide a fully integrated system, tailored to your 
requirements.</p>

<p>MDS has specialized in Office Refreshment Management Systems for over 28 years. Starting off primarily as an in-office sales tracking and 
accounting package, MDS has expanded into support of hand-held devices 
and e-Commerce.</p>

<p>MDS strives to continue adding innovative new products and systems to its current catolog, all to help improve accuracy, efficiency, and profitability.  With a modular system, you get what your company needs now with the flexibility of adding more systems later as your company grows.  The MDS system is an affordable operating solution for your OCS business.</p>




</div>


