        <li>&rsaquo; Flexible Multi-Tier Customer Pricing.</li>
        <li>&rsaquo; Easy Integration with Other Major Software Applications.</li>
        <li>&rsaquo; Equipment Rental Billing and Location/Movement Tracking.</li>
        <li>&rsaquo; Inventory Control over Warehouse and Truck Inventories.</li>
        <li>&rsaquo; Control Cash Flow with integrated Purchase Order, A/R, A/P and General Ledger Systems.</li>
        <li>&rsaquo; Vendor Purchase Orders automatically update Accounts Payable.</li>
